abstract.text: Embed the Avaya Experience Platform™ (AXP) Messaging View in your Application.

The main view for the Messaging UI. This view is responsible for displaying messages, sending messages, and displaying the typing indicator. It also provides a way to add attachments to messages. This view is also supported Rich Media. The view will automatically update when new messages are received. The view is designed to be used in a SwiftUI application.
